<h2>Google Business Profile: Your Most Important Asset</h2>
<p>Your Google Business Profile (GBP) accounts for <a href="https://americanmedspa.org/blog/top-10-google-ranking-factors-for-medical-spas">over 30% of local ranking signals</a>. It is the first thing patients see when they search "med spa near me" or "[treatment] in [city]."</p>
<h3>Claim and Verify</h3>
<p>If you have not claimed your GBP listing, do it today. Go to <a href="https://business.google.com">business.google.com</a>, search for your med spa, and follow the verification process. Google may verify by phone, email, postcard, or video.</p>
<p>An unclaimed profile means someone else could edit your listing. It also means you cannot respond to reviews, post updates, or add services.</p>
